data.name: pattern_DocuSignComplete
data.value:

^You receive this email because you are a registered user of the "${__VirtualRootPath}":"${__VirtualRootPath}" portal.^ Alternative translation

Prijavite se na svoj DocuSign račun za više informacija.

data.name: pattern_EditorMentions

h1. "$ __ AuthorName": "$ __ AuthorUrl" vas je spomenuo u komentaru dokumenta
Ovo je poruka e-pošte koja vas obavještava da vas je "$ __ AuthorName" spomenuo: "$ __ AuthorUrl" u komentaru na dokument "$ DocumentTitle": "$ DocumentURL":
$ Poruka

data.name: pattern_MailMergeEnd
data.value:
h1. Mailing completed
This is an email notification to inform you that you have requested the mailing of $MailsCount messages and the process is now complete. $Message
The successfully sent mail messages can be found in your "Sent":"$__VirtualRootPath/addons/mail/#sent" folder of the Mail module.
^You receive this email because you are a registered user of the "${__VirtualRootPath}":"${__VirtualRootPath}" portal.^

data.name: pattern_ShareDocument
data.value:
h1. Odobren pristup dokumentu: "$DocumentTitle":"$DocumentURL"
$__DateTime "$__AuthorName":"$__AuthorUrl" vam je odobrio pristup dokumentu "$DocumentTitle":"$DocumentURL" sa sljedećim pristupnim pravima: "$AccessRights".
$Message

data.name: pattern_ShareFolder
data.value:
h1. Access granted to folder: "$DocumentTitle":"$DocumentURL"
$__DateTime "$__AuthorName":"$__AuthorUrl" granted you the access to the "$DocumentTitle":"$DocumentURL" folder with the following access rights: "$AccessRights".
$Message
